{"title":"JavaScript —— 安全","date":"2019-11-17T11:50:30.981Z","thumbnail":"https://s2.ax1x.com/2019/11/17/Mrqf1A.md.jpg","link":"2019/11/17/safety","updated":"2019-11-17T15:54:08.264Z","content":"<h2 id=\"常见web前端攻击方式\">常见web前端攻击方式<a href=\"2019/11/17/safety#常见web前端攻击方式\"></a></h2><ul>\n<li><p>XSS跨站请求攻击</p>\n<p><strong>例子：</strong>一个博客网站，我发表一篇博客，其中嵌入script脚本。脚本内容为获取cookie，发送到我的服务器。所以发表的博客只有有人查看，就能轻松获得访问者的cookie</p>\n<p><strong>预防：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>替换特殊字符，如<code>&lt;</code>变成<code>&amp;lt</code>，<code>&gt;</code>变成<code>&amp;gt</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>XSRF跨站请求伪造</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n","next":{"title":"性能优化","link":"2019/11/15/Performance-optimization"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2019/11/17/safety/","toc":[{"title":"常见web前端攻击方式","id":"常见web前端攻击方式","index":"1"}]}